title: Westerly kindergarten registration begins Jan. 6
text:
Levi King, Chariho basketball, Senior: King scored 42 points and grabbed 24 points in two games as the Chargers opened the season with wins against Ponaganset and Division I South Kingstown.

Chas Morgan, Westerly basketball, Senior: Morgan scored 15 points as Westerly started the season with a loss to defending state champion North Kingstown. Morgan had six rebounds in the setback.
